divs: Sighting Details1st viewer was outside. Saw the UFO. called for 2nd viewer. Second viewer saw the streak (tail) of the UFO disappearing. Appeared to be gliding at a high speed. 1st viewer was just looking up at the night sky. Was uncertain what the object was at first. Object moved (streaked) away at a very high rate of speed.

Summary: White triangle. Moved away at high speed. 2nd observer saw streak. Flying lower than a typical jet.
